Products.RichDescription: Perfect pack size What's the best bit about Birds Eye Golden Crunch Beer Batter Chips?They're perfectly crunchy on the outside and deliciously fluffy on the inside!It's our delicious crispy coating that makes our beer batter chips such as surefire crowd pleaser! We start with local Tassie spuds, coat with our secret recipe batter, then gently cook each batch in 100% canola oil.And the second best bit? Our fun new pack size is the perfect fit for your freezer... and the oven! Throw the whole lot in for a tasty treat everyone loves. Serve them hot straight from the oven then stand back to avoid the rush!
